name: Out Of Control
description:
When a heavy burden weighs you down. The mind will be out of control. Though the mind is the key to self-control. Everything seems possible. It's like an attack from another dimension controlling the earth. If we don't fight back, the result: No more people, no more life.

Emotions are meaningless. Everything becomes useless and self-defeating.Calm your mind to deal with your emotions, so you can choose the best solution.
